data.description: WOW - GET YOUR GOLF CART READY! Adorable 3 Bedroom 2 Bath home just one mile from HISTORIC DOWN TOWN SENOIA with easy GOLF CART TRAIL ACCESS! Exterior painted, 30 year architectural roof, nearly new HVAC and furnace, etc.! 1465 Finished Square Footage with TWO CAR GARAGE, LARGE STORAGE SHED, and HUGE FENCED BACK YARD! Welcoming covered front porch invites you into this adorable home leading you to the right for all the bedrooms and baths or to the left for all the living, kitchen and dining areas. Warm brick fireplace in the family room looks all the way through the kitchen and dining area through grand double doors to the outside. All the bedrooms have ceiling fans and plenty of closet space. The primary bedroom on the main level has lots of room and great views of the spacious backyard. The laundry/pantry includes a huge 10'x10' room and additional two door shelved closet off the kitchen. The bedrooms are spacious with walk in closets. There is also a hall work area/office that could be converted back to a large linen closet if desired. THE TERRIFIC BACKYARD IS HUGE. PRIVATE AND COMPLETELY FENCED. STORAGE GALORE between the STAND UP CRAWL SPACE, STORAGE SHED, AND TWO CAR GARAGE! AND ... THE LOCATION CANNOT BE BEAT! Walking distance to down town Senoia in a beautiful subdivision with great neighbors! GREAT LOCATION! WONDERFUL SCHOOLS! TERRIFIC HOME! FANTASTIC PRICE! FANTASTIC NEIGHBORS! CALL TODAY BECAUSE THIS ONE SHOULD NOT LAST LONG!!
